  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A short automation game with deep lore but little space!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build</strong> your production lines!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271960/extras/6cbb852f34b70f79a47e91ffc4be805c.poster.avif?t=1774558341\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271960/extras/6cbb852f34b70f79a47e91ffc4be805c.webm?t=1774558341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271960/extras/6cbb852f34b70f79a47e91ffc4be805c.mp4?t=1774558341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlock</strong> new areas and powerful machines!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271960/extras/29e5b06f1ef00b8002807470c7066acf.poster.avif?t=1774558341\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271960/extras/29e5b06f1ef00b8002807470c7066acf.webm?t=1774558341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271960/extras/29e5b06f1ef00b8002807470c7066acf.mp4?t=1774558341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the <strong>in-game Wiki</strong> to get information about everything!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271960/extras/59bfc9c6ac2b7b883039a5051f96c487.poster.avif?t=1774558341\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271960/extras/59bfc9c6ac2b7b883039a5051f96c487.webm?t=1774558341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271960/extras/59bfc9c6ac2b7b883039a5051f96c487.mp4?t=1774558341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use <strong>InfiniBoxes™</strong> to cheat space!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271960/extras/2374cf4e317d2f2ad01e061f81bd417a.poster.avif?t=1774558341\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271960/extras/2374cf4e317d2f2ad01e061f81bd417a.webm?t=1774558341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271960/extras/2374cf4e317d2f2ad01e061f81bd417a.mp4?t=1774558341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271960/extras/3acbc50d6328725a63a8fcaf0469eb34.poster.avif?t=1774558341\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271960/extras/3acbc50d6328725a63a8fcaf0469eb34.webm?t=1774558341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271960/extras/3acbc50d6328725a63a8fcaf0469eb34.mp4?t=1774558341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271960/extras/82d23d0fc7de529ec17fce434afaf3c1.poster.avif?t=1774558341\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271960/extras/82d23d0fc7de529ec17fce434afaf3c1.webm?t=1774558341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271960/extras/82d23d0fc7de529ec17fce434afaf3c1.mp4?t=1774558341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can <strong>you</strong> figure out a way to build an efficient factory with the limited space you have?</p>",
